<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>日常生活法律 on 曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B/</link><description>Recent content in 日常生活法律 on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:30:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>婚没结成，彩礼能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%BD%A9%E7%A4%BC%E8%BF%94%E8%BF%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%BD%A9%E7%A4%BC%E8%BF%94%E8%BF%98/</guid><description>谈了两年，彩礼给了，婚期定了，临门一脚分手了。十八万八的彩礼——能要回来多少？</description></item><item><title>遗产怎么继承？没有遗嘱的情况下，钱和房子归谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF/</guid><description>人走了，没有留遗嘱。配偶、孩子、父母——谁先拿、谁后拿、谁拿多少。法律早就排好了顺序。</description></item><item><title>帮人转了一笔账，结果成了犯罪——帮信罪离你有多近</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%B8%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BD%AA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 03:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%B8%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BD%AA/</guid><description>朋友让你帮忙转一笔钱，或者借你的银行卡用一下——你可能正在犯帮信罪。这个罪名近年来起诉人数已经冲到前三了。</description></item><item><title>买到了假货，除了退货还能让他赔你三倍</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</guid><description>买到假货别光退货。法律规定经营者欺诈的退一赔三，最低赔五百。很多人不知道这条，白白吃亏。</description></item><item><title>出了交通事故，对方全责但不赔钱，你拿他一点办法都没有？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E7%90%86%E8%B5%94/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E7%90%86%E8%B5%94/</guid><description>被撞了，对方全责，但他就是不赔钱。没有保险？司机跑了？这些情况下你的钱谁来赔？</description></item><item><title>楼上漏水把你家淹了，对方不赔怎么办？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4/</guid><description>楼上漏水泡了你家天花板，对方说不是他的责任。物业、开发商、楼上邻居——到底该找谁？</description></item><item><title>离婚的时候，房子到底归谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A6%BB%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A6%BB%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2/</guid><description>婚前买房、婚后还贷、父母出资——离婚时房子怎么分，比你想象的复杂得多。</description></item><item><title>借条怎么写才有效？少写一个字，钱可能就要不回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</guid><description>借条和欠条一字之差，法律后果天差地别。借钱出去之前花三分钟看完这篇，省掉将来三年的麻烦。</description></item><item><title>租房押金被扣了？房东敢扣你钱，你就敢让他吐出来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</guid><description>退房的时候房东找各种理由扣你押金——墙壁脏了、家电旧了、地板花了。哪些该你赔，哪些不该？律师说清楚。</description></item><item><title>别人欠你钱不还？不用打官司也能把钱要回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</guid><description>欠钱不还，一定要打官司吗？律师告诉你一条更快的路——支付令。15天出结果，费用只要诉讼的十分之一。</description></item><item><title>朋友借钱你担保？一个签名，一套房子没了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</guid><description>帮朋友在借条上签了个名，结果被执行了一套房子。担保这件事，99%的人都没当回事——等出事的时候，已经晚了。</description></item></channel></rss>